 Syntax:  .quote
	  .quote -l
	  .quote -s

Results:  Typed once it by itself will turn the quote_of_the_day, at
	  login, off.  Typed again by itself will turn the
	  quote_of_the_day, at login, back on again.
	  Typed with the -l flag will show you a random, normal size quote
	  Typed with the -s flag will show you a random, small size quote

